&lt;h2 data-usually-unique-id=&quot;044234883370604133046166&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zqz90zkz74zz76zeez80zz68zz89zz88zvqz86zuxlz73zexxz80zz73z6d6z72zz79zsz77z&quot;&gt;Compensation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;US Zone 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$236,300&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$319,700 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;US Zone 2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$212,700&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$287,700 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;US Zone 3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$189,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$255,800 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dropbox is seeking an exceptional Technical Program Manager (TPM) to join our team. As part of the CTO team, you will lead enterprise wide programs driven out of the CTO org or some of the highest priority initiatives at the company. You will collaborate cross-functionally with teams to align on strategy and requirements, define and execute on clear roadmaps, drive alignment with product and company priorities, and own the end-to-end execution of your programs. The ideal candidate has strong technical experience, organized and detail oriented, able to use their influence to drive results for their team with a sense of urgency and ownership and is a adaptable team player who is able to drive ambiguous challenging programs forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;Our Engineering Career Framework is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attrlink url author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;attrlink&quot; href=&quot;https://dropbox.github.io/dbx-career-framework/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-target-href=&quot;https://dropbox.github.io/dbx-career-framework/&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;viewable by anyone outside the company&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt; and describes what’s expected for our engineers at each of our career levels. Check out our blog post on this topic and more &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attrlink url author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;attrlink&quot; href=&quot;https://dropbox.tech/culture/sharing-our-engineering-career-framework-with-the-world&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-target-href=&quot;https://dropbox.tech/culture/sharing-our-engineering-career-framework-with-the-world&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Program Leadership:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will drive the development, alignment, and execution of strategic engineering initiatives, defining clear roadmaps and ensuring successful delivery across cross-functional teams. You must be able to manage ambitious timelines, proactively identify and mitigate risks and issues, and lead the successful execution of complex, cross-functional engineering programs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Stakeholder Management:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will build trusted partnerships with cross-functional stakeholders at all levels of the organization to align priorities, remove roadblocks, and drive collective success.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Executive Communication:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will communicate program goals, progress, and outcomes clearly and confidently across teams and to executive leadership, providing transparency and fostering alignment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Leadership Through Influence:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will collaborate effectively with leaders to guide decisions, resolve conflicts, and ensure progress toward shared goals through influence and operational excellence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Operational Excellence:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will identify and implement scalable processes, tools, and best practices that improve execution efficiency, predictability, and cross-team collaboration across the engineering organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Data-Driven Execution:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will use metrics and KPIs to assess program health, measure impact, and drive data-informed decisions that ensure successful outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Culture &amp;amp; Mentorship:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; You will foster a culture of accountability, collaboration, and continuous improvement, while mentoring peers and emerging TPMs to elevate program management excellence across the organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;listtype-bullet listindent1 list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;12+ years of Technical Program Management experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; driving complex, cross-functional, and highly technical programs in a related industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or equivalent technical discipline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;; advanced degree preferred or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Deep technical aptitude&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; with the ability to understand and influence technical architectures, discuss system design, reliability, and scalability tradeoffs, and connect technical decisions to business impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Exceptional communication and executive presence,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; with demonstrated ability to influence and align senior leaders and technical teams. Skilled at presenting to large audiences and managing high-stakes communication under pressure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Proven success delivering large-scale, enterprise level, cross-functional programs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; with significant technical complexity, using expert program management practices, structured problem solving, and process improvement to drive predictable outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ownership of end-to-end execution,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; from strategy and roadmap definition through delivery and post-launch measurement, ensuring technical and business goals are met.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt;Track record of scaling impact beyond direct scope,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvovz84zz73zyqz86zez79znz72zz87z5wraz75z1gnz67zjz65zq8z81ziv3z71z&quot;&gt; mentoring TPMs and engineering peers, and contributing to the evolution of program management frameworks and best practices across the organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/h2&gt;
